OL,3,CShocking images show child in car
OL,4,Cwhere nobody was wearing a seatbelt
OL,6,FPolice officers were left 'shocked'
OL,7,Fafter spotting a sleeping one-year-old
OL,8,Fchild not in their car seat and both
OL,9,Fthe driver and passenger not wearing
OL,10,Fseatbelts.
OL,12,FOfficers from Lancashire Road Policing
OL,13,FUnit said a fully marked car was
OL,14,Fwaiting at a red light in Blackburn on
OL,15,F29 April when the offending vehicle
OL,16,Fpulled up alongside.
OL,18,FThe traffic officers immediately
OL,19,Fnoticed the empty car seat and the
OL,20,Fdriver failing to use a seatbelt.
